# Example: Mullvad OpenVPN Configuration
# =================================================================
# Note: Mullvad is deprecating OpenVPN. WireGuard is recommended.
#
# client
# dev tun
# proto udp
# remote se-sto-ovpn-001.relays.mullvad.net 1194
# resolv-retry infinite
# nobind
# persist-key
# persist-tun
# remote-cert-tls server
# auth SHA512
# cipher AES-256-CBC
# verb 3
# auth-user-pass
# ca mullvad_ca.crt
# tun-ipv6
# script-security 2

# =================================================================
# Notes
# =================================================================
# - Keep your keys secret! Never commit them to version control.
# - The .gitignore file is configured to exclude all .conf files
#   (except .example files) to prevent accidental commits.
# - WireGuard is generally recommended over OpenVPN for:
#   * Better performance (faster speeds)
#   * Stronger cryptography
#   * Simpler configuration
#   * Lower battery usage on mobile devices
# - Use OpenVPN only if:
#   * Your VPN provider doesn't support WireGuard
#   * You need TCP mode (for restrictive networks)
#   * You have specific OpenVPN requirements
